msgid "**Cause:** Invalid redirect URI configuration in Keycloak."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Clogin-flow.md:264
msgid "**Fix:** Verify the `ronl-business-api` client in Keycloak Admin has:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Clogin-flow.md:265
msgid ""
"Valid Redirect URIs: https://acc.mijn.open-regels.nl/*\n"
"Web Origins: +"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Clogin-flow.md:270
msgid "\"Terug naar inlogkeuze\" requires two clicks"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Clogin-flow.md:272
msgid ""
"**Cause:** The `/auth` route (`AuthCallback.tsx`) is an intermediate step in "
"the browser history. Navigating back once lands on `/auth`, which "
"immediately redirects to Keycloak again."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Clogin-flow.md:274
msgid ""
"**Fix:** The cancel link in `login.ftl` uses `history.go(-2)` to skip past `/"
"auth` in a single click."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Clogin-flow.md:276
msgid "Wrong municipality shown after login"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Clogin-flow.md:278
msgid ""
"**Cause:** The user account has an incorrect `municipality` attribute in "
"Keycloak."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Clogin-flow.md:280
msgid ""
"**Fix:** In Keycloak Admin Console → Users → select the user → Attributes → "
"set `municipality` to the correct value, then log out and back in."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Clogin-flow.md:282
msgid "Caseworker banner not showing"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Clogin-flow.md:284
msgid ""
"**Cause:** The `__medewerker__` `login_hint` is not being passed, or the "
"`login.ftl` template version on the server is outdated."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cuser-guide%5Clogin-flow.md:286
msgid ""
"**Fix:** Verify that `sessionStorage` contains `selected_idp = medewerker` "
"before `/auth` loads (check DevTools → Application → Session Storage). If "
"the theme file is outdated, redeploy the theme and restart the Keycloak "
"container (see [Keycloak Deployment]{1})."
msgstr ""

